item.title: Can some one please help me?
item.dc:creator: @iceburster iceburster
item.description:
@iceburster wrote:

Hmm, try using a different runserver.bat.

EDIT:
Or use this for your compiler. It compiles then runs the server.
Code:
@echo off
title COMPILER
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_02\bin\javac.exe” -cp . *.java
“C:\Program Files\Java\jre1.6.0_02\bin/java.exe” server
pause
